data.description:
Great home for entertaining one of the main things owners love about their home.  Covered patio where the guests gather to enjoy football games.  Roof approximately a year old.   Beautifully updated kitchen, new floors.  A MUST to see in person.  Decorative lights in the kitchen and dining area.
Neighbors are great.  Huge living room with wood burning brick fireplace.  Nice back yard to install a workshop.  Possibly a fourth bedroom if not an office area.
